Task 2
You are required to create basic To-Do list app using HTML, CSS and JavaScript. It should implement the following functions:
1. Add tasks
2. Delete tasks
3. Mark task as done
For reference:
You list can look something like this- https://drive.google.com/file/d/1kuaXex1oeRun7CDOV8yuQ9oKPDuIfUNq/view?usp=sharing

Make sure you make it look attractive and neat at the same time, since this is a frontend task. You can use the Bootstrap framework to make your webpage look better.
Resources for learning:
1.https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML
2.https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS
3.https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript
4.https://www.w3schools.com/
5.https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.0/getting-started/introduction/
6. https://youtu.be/pN6jk0uUrD8

